CONFLUENCE
In simple terms "confluence" is central repository where you can share or find information to do your job
Confluence is a tool developed by atlassian designed for team collaboration and project documentation

Key aspects of Confluence include :
  1) Spaces and Pages : Organizes work into "spaces" for different teams or projects, containing "pages" for content.
  2) Collaboration Tools : Features real-time editing, comments, and whiteboards to facilitate teamwork.
  3) Structured Content : Uses templates and macros to streamline documentation and make information easy to find.
  4) Centralized Source of Truth : Acts as an intranet or repository, ensuring everyone in the organization has access to up-to-date information. 
